dct_title_s: Spain 1:10,000. Mataro city plan. A.M.S. M981
dct_description_sm: Map shows military and coast guard headquarters. Some streets and buildings are named. "Prepared from Europe B - 24 - MG - 33; Spanish map 1:50,000, 393." "Army Map Service, U. S. Army, Washington, D. C. 114982. 1943. 3-43." Military grid. Alternate title: Mataro city plan. Prepared from Europe B-24-MG-33; Spanish map 1:50,000, 393. Projection approximate. AMS 1.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
